The FileUpload component provides a simple yet flexible means of adding support for multipart
    file upload functionality to servlets and web applications. - http://commons.apache.org/fileupload/ - scm:svn:http://svn.apache.org/repos/asf/commons/proper/fileupload/trunk

modules.moduleName: Guava: Google Core Libraries for Java
modules.extraDescription:
Guava is a suite of core and expanded libraries that include
    utility classes, google's collections, io classes, and much
    much more.

    Guava has only one code dependency - javax.annotation,
    per the JSR-305 spec.

Commons Logging is a thin adapter allowing configurable bridging to other,
    well known logging systems. - http://commons.apache.org/logging - scm:svn:http://svn.apache.org/repos/asf/commons/proper/logging/tags/commons-logging-1.1.1

Apache Commons Lang, a package of Java utility classes for the
  classes that are in java.lang's hierarchy, or are considered to be so
  standard as to justify existence in java.lang. - http://commons.apache.org/proper/commons-lang/ - scm:svn:http://svn.apache.org/repos/asf/commons/proper/lang/trunk

The Amazon Web Services SDK for Java provides Java APIs for building software on AWSâ€™ cost-effective, scalable, and reliable infrastructure products. The AWS Java SDK allows developers to code against APIs for all of Amazon's infrastructure web services (Amazon S3, Amazon EC2, Amazon SQS, Amazon Relational Database Service, Amazon AutoScaling, etc). - https://aws.amazon.com/sdkforjava

Data Mapper package is a high-performance data binding package
built on Jackson JSON processor - http://jackson.codehaus.org

The codec package contains simple encoder and decoders for
     various formats such as Base64 and Hexadecimal.  In addition to these
     widely used encoders and decoders, the codec package also maintains a
     collection of phonetic encoding utilities. - http://commons.apache.org/codec/ - scm:svn:http://svn.apache.org/repos/asf/commons/proper/codec/trunk
Jackson is a high-performance JSON processor (parser, generator) - http://jackson.codehaus.org

Commons-IO contains utility classes, stream implementations, file filters, file comparators and endian classes. - http://commons.apache.org/io/ - scm:svn:http://svn.apache.org/repos/asf/commons/proper/io/trunk
